import '../stylesheets/discoverProjects.css'; import { Link } from "react-router-dom"; import {toggle} from './projectsJS.js'; export function DiscoverProjects() { function toggle(x) { if (getComputedStyle(document.getElementsByClassName('cover')[x]).getPropertyValue('background-color') == 'transparent') document.getElementsByClassName('cover')[x].style.setProperty('background-color','var(--color-primary)') else document.getElementsByClassName('cover')[x].style.setProperty('background-color','transparent') } return ( <>

SOURCING CREATE PROJECTS

The 4D Cycle

To effectively lead projects using the 4D Cycle, it's crucial to have a deep understanding of each stage.
Disover

Reorient to see, through the lens of Christ, those most affected by the problem

Learn More
Develop

Recognize that God establishes our steps to develop the solution, and co-develop with the Holy Spirit.

Learn More
Demonstrate
